04a5d","tid":1425820,"uid":49588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T00:48:22.000Z","msg":"由於現時的香港警察已經再不是以保護香港及香港人，而我們亦沒有軍隊，我們本地香港人可否行使權利，集體罷免現時香港的所有警察職務？<br />\n<br />\n再由我們本地香港人成立一支香港臨時的自衛軍，直到情況穩定為止。"},{"pid":"94442a51d8939ccebf4341620788a4eb307a0000","tid":1425820,"uid":49588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T00:48:59.000Z","msg":"否則本地香港人的生命與財產都沒有得到保障"},{"pid":"efc9a8ef7410506b29b1bdd705a1169bf840e200","tid":1425820,"uid":33709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T00:50:46.000Z","msg":"老婆講得好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf667af7b322f5f9b273016e2e655a1d4a2418ca","tid":1425820,"uid":251292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T00:59:39.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ff1649b8878860d8903413000f9cb44c305c3fdb","tid":1425820,"uid":41901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T01:00:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e32a0c94cf1d0fa9feb6bf02a032ca687d68707d","tid":1425820,"uid":12444,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T01:11:34.000Z","msg":"立場姐姐真係好有心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6cf4c471f1acbf7dc7bbcab3c43f6dc49795a6dc","tid":1425820,"uid":53369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T06:55:39.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"add576523edceb22a53e7aefd58a4ee71f3eeb6c","tid":1425820,"uid":34705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T06:57:49.000Z","msg":"好長，但請各位睇晒佢"},{"pid":"a0c3e98a6a114a3c9fc490ff793076bd79231943","tid":1425820,"uid":53369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T07:22:26.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"3060394a5aec5e91cdf26099b58d5724977c566e","ti